item.title: CVE-2023-41940|2024-09-27T19:48:04.346Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20tap%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins TAP Plugin 2.3 and earlier does not escape TAP file contents, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers able to control TAP file contents.
